/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 161, \"end\": 174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelby_McEwen\", \"score\": 0.9999970370593713, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shelby McEwen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelby_McEwen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelby_McEwen\"}, {\"begin\": 201, \"end\": 212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamish_Kerr\", \"score\": 0.9999998928324261, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hamish Kerr\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamish_Kerr\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamish_Kerr\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bar\", \"from\": 143, \"to\": 150}, {\"ngram\": \"world indoor champion\", \"from\": 179, \"to\": 200}, {\"ngram\": \"New Zealand\", \"from\": 216, \"to\": 227}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two high jumpers, who could have decided to tie and both get a gold medal, instead put fans through an interminable jump-off for the gold at the Paris Olympics on Saturday.\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 424, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The two high jumpers\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 268}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 325}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 339, \"to\": 343}, {\"ngram\": \"an interminable jump-off\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 376}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 389}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 411}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 415, \"to\": 423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two men had 11 straight misses - so many that there wasn't enough room on the scoreboard for all the Xs - in regulation and the jump-off.\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 567, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The two men\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 437}, {\"ngram\": \"11 straight misses\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 460}, {\"ngram\": \"enough room\", \"from\": 489, \"to\": 5