\"end\": 1311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9997572679473911, \"rank\": 0.0002425213169951534, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so much respect\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I always thought that to add to the story and to be able to be given the chance to actually do the jump-off would be so amazing,\\\" Kerr said.\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1457, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the story\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1396}, {\"ngram\": \"the jump-off\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1424}, {\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knew straight away that we were going to make history and we did that.\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1531, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am pretty sure Shelby was in the same mindset because we just looked at each other and it was pretty simple,\\\" Kerr added.\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1657, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1551, \"end\": 1557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carroll_Shelby\", \"score\": 0.8395239396876213, \"rank\": 0.1911512617162034, \"text\": \"Shelby\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carroll_Shelby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carroll_Shelby\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same mindset\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1581}, {\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We both just nodded and off we went.\\\"\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1696, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Added McEwen, \\\"We talked to each other, and he was like, 'Let us jump off.'\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1773, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I was like, 'I am all for it.'\\\"\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1809, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kerr celebrated by running around the field in the center of the Stade de France deliriously.\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1904, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1876, \"end\": 1891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 1876, \"end\": 1891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1815}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1854}, {\"ngram\": \"the center\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1868}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They both missed at 2.38 in the first round of the jump-off, another two misses at 2.36 and McEwen missed at 2.34 before Kerr finally ended the first competition of the night only moments before the women's 4x400 relay concluded the last session of track and field at the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 2194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1998, \"end\": 2004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_McEwen\", \"score\": 0.999999987066076, \"rank\": 1.2934003943511358e-08, \"text\": \"McEwen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_McEwen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_McEwen\"}, {\"begin\": 2178, \"end\": 2193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first round\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1949}, {\"ngram\": \"the jump-off\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1965}, {\"ngram\": \"another two misses\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1985}, {\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2031}, {\"ngram\": \"the first competition\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2067}, {\"ngram\": \"the night\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2080}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's 4x400 relay\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2124}, {\"ngram\": \"the last session\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2151}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2160}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If I had not cleared that jump or one very soon, we probably still would be out there,\\\" Kerr said.\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2295, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that jump\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2227}, {\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2289}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McEwen said he thought \\\"we both got a little fatigued there at the end,\\\" adding that he was thinking about the $50,000 prize for first place.\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2297, \"end\": 2303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_McEwen\", \"score\": 0.999999987066076, \"rank\": 1.2934003943511358e-08, \"text\": \"McEwen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_McEwen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_McEwen\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2367}, {\"ngram\": \"the $50,000 prize\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2421}, {\"ngram\": \"first place\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Most definitely, I got a family to feed.\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2480, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a family\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2471}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, hey, we are going to get back to the drawing boards and get better.\\\"\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2554, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the drawing boards\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier, Tamberi failed on all three of his attempts at 2.27 - only the second height of the competition.\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2661, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tamberi\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2572}, {\"ngram\": \"his attempts\", \"from\": 2596, \"to\": 2608}, {\"ngram\": \"only the second height\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2641}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2660}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He covered his face with his hands in disappointment and then Barshim came over to console his good friend.\", \"from\": 2662, \"to\": 2769, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his face\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2681}, {\"ngram\": \"his hands\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2696}, {\"ngram\": \"disappointment\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2714}, {\"ngram\": \"Barshim\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2731}, {\"ngram\": \"his good friend\", \"from\": 2753, \"to\": 2768}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tamberi had been bothered by a series of physical issues over the last few days.\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2851, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tamberi\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2778}, {\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2808}, {\"ngram\": \"physical issues\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2827}, {\"ngram\": \"the last few days\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2850}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was hospitalized due to kidney stones and had a fever of 38.8 Celsius (101.8 Fahrenheit).\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2944, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"kidney stones\", \"from\": 2879, \"to\": 2892}, {\"ngram\": \"a fever\", \"from\": 2901, \"to\": 2908}, {\"ngram\": \"38.8 Celsius\", \"from\": 2912, \"to\": 2924}, {\"ngram\": \"101.8 Fahrenheit\", \"from\": 2926, \"to\": 2942}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he vowed to compete no matter what.\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 2984, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When it was over, and Tamberi had finished 11th in the 12-man final, he went over and cried with his team in the stands.\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 3106, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tamberi\", \"from\": 3008, \"to\": 3015}, {\"ngram\": \"11th\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3033}, {\"ngram\": \"his team\", \"from\": 3083, \"to\": 3091}, {\"ngram\": \"the stands\", \"from\": 3095, \"to\": 3105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"___ AP Olympics: https://apnews.com/hub/2024-paris-olympic-games \\u00a92025 BellMedia All Rights Reserved\", \"from\": 3108, \"to\": 3210, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3113, \"end\": 3115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999989125564299, \"rank\": 1.0851106646411857e-06, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"https://apnews.com/hub/2024-paris-olympic-games\", \"from\": 3125, \"to\": 3172}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00a9\", \"from\": 3173, \"to\": 3174}, {\"ngram\": \"BellMedia\", \"from\": 3179, \"to\": 3188}, {\"ngram\": \"All Rights\", \"from\": 3189, \"to\": 3199}]}]}"